                "invention-title": [
                    "Wind-light hydrogen storage water lifting system",
                    "一种风光氢储提水系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a wind-light hydrogen storage water lifting system, which comprises a load end used for power consumption and internally provided with a controller used for controlling the operation process of the wind-light hydrogen storage water lifting system; the fan is used for collecting wind energy and generating electricity through the wind energy; the photovoltaic panel is used for collecting solar energy and carrying out solar power generation, and a photovoltaic module is arranged in the photovoltaic panel and used for detecting solar radiation to obtain solar radiation intensity P; the water electrolysis system is used for collecting distilled water generated by heating in the power generation process; the hydrogen storage system is used for storing hydrogen energy; the fuel cell is used for consuming hydrogen energy to supply power; the water pump is used for supplying water; the electric quantity detector is used for detecting the electric quantity reserve condition of the load end to obtain real-time electric quantity reserve D; the air velocity sensor is used for measuring the air velocity to obtain the air flow velocity K; therefore, the stability of a power supply system in a remote area can be improved by controlling the water pump to supply water through wind and light complementation by driving the water pump to lift water through wind energy and solar energy hydrogen production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种风光氢储提水系统，包括：负载端，用以进行耗电，其内设置有控制器，用以控制风光储氢提水系统的作业过程；风机，用以采集风能并通过风能进行发电；光伏板，用以采集太阳能并进行太阳光发电，其内设置有光伏组件，用以对太阳辐射进行检测以得到太阳辐射强度P；电解水系统，用以收集发电过程中发热产生的蒸馏水；储氢系统，用以储存氢能；燃料电池，用以消耗氢能以进行供电；水泵，用以进行供水；电量检测器，用以检测负载端的电量储备情况以获得实时电量储备D；空气流速传感器，用以测量空气流速以获得空气流动速度K。从而能够通过风能和太阳能制氢驱动水泵提水进而通过风光互补控制水泵供水以提高偏远地区供电系统的稳定性。"
                }
            ]
